CloudyTasks is a open source online study organizer written in Python and running on the Google App Engine. 

You can either use my public instance at http://cloudytasks.appspot.com or take the source code and run your own instance.

Features:
- Todo list
- Class overview
- Add the index of a pdf file to a class to check off chapters and track your progress
- Multilingual -> English and German right now ( feel free to add translations )

Coming soon:
- Calender